attributes.background:
Considering the fact that other sports such as rugby league rugby union  and championship football allow safe standing at stadiums; some using premier league football grounds; 

Isn’t it time to allow standing at football grounds for premier league teams, you have fans diving on the stage at rock concerts the stars even throw themselves into the crowd and call it crowd surfing 

It is ludicrous to ban standing on the terraces because it is deemed unsafe when all the other sports are allowed to have standing it is double standards to carry on with this ban as it stands please let us have a review
